PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2010-05832010-05-13,  ,  EC,  , 
ActCanada Water Act
SubjectCanada-Manitoba Memorandum of Understanding Respecting Lake Winnipeg and the Lake Winnipeg Basin
PrecisCanada-Manitoba MEMORANDUM OF UNDERSTANDING RESPECTING LAKE WINNIPEG AND THE LAKE WINNIPEG BASIN to a) identify joint priorities for coordinated science activities relating to Lake Winnipeg, b) coordinate information sharing of federal and provincial programs and activities relating to Lake Winnipeg, and c) establish a federal provincial steering committee to oversee implementation of specific actions outlined in the memorandum.
